      "url": "https://cdn.misoenergy.org/20251209%20Markets%20Committee%20of%20the%20BOD%20Item%2005a%20MISO%20Detailed%20Response%20to%202024%20IMM%20SOM%20Report730264.pdf",
      "published_date": "2025-12-09T00:00:00.000Z",
      "text": "Midcontinent Independent \nSystem Operator, Inc.\n317.249-5400\nwww.misoenergy.org\n720 City Center Drive\nCarmel, Indiana 46032\n2985 Ames Crossing Road\nEagan, Minnesota 55121\n1700 Centerview Drive\nLittle Rock, AR 72211\nTO: MARKETS COMMITTEE OF THE BOARD OF DIRECTORS\nFROM: ZAK JOUNDI, EXECUTIVE DIRECTOR MARKETS AND GRID STRATEGY\nSUBJECT: MISO’S RESPONSE TO THE IMM 2024 STATE OF THE MARKET REPORT\nDATE: NOVEMBER 25, 2025\nPlease find attached MISO’s response to the annual 2024 State of the Market (SOM) Report by \nthe Independent Market Monitor, which Dr. Patton reviewed with you in June. The report \nconcluded that MISO’s energy and ancillary services markets performed competitively in 2024. \nThe IMM made four new recommendations to enhance the markets. MISO agrees with all four\nissues identified by the IMM and the recommended solution for one with the other three pending \nfurther evaluation. MISO is actively working on one of the four recommendations and plans to \nwork on the other three withi",
